name: Sui Monster
description: This is Sui Chain meme token. We developed it by discovering the future development potential of Suichain and the positive aspects of meme tokens. I think it would be better if SUIMON did its best to grow into the meme token representing Suichain and thereby revitalize Suichain's meme token market. We will contribute to the future development of SuiChain and create a good meme token market by maximizing the strengths of meme tokens.
